    <span>anisa, an information aggregator made by skuqre. more projects at <a href="https://skuqre.github.io/">skuqre.github.io</a></span>
    <span>you're running on commit <code><a href="/" id="commit" target="_blank"></a></code>. you can always report issues at the <a href="https://github.com/skuqre/anisa/issues">GitHub</a>.</span>
